{
  "texts": [
    "Signal peptides were removed from sequences predicted to contain them.",
    "A set of 14 representative CuSOD and 2 FeSOD proteins were manually selected for experimental screening, including eukaryotic, viral and bacterial proteins predicted to not contain signal peptides, and bacterial proteins with predicted signal peptides removed.",
    "Rounds 2 and 3 CuSOD.",
    "All eukaryotic transcriptomes available from the NCBI Transcriptome Shotgun Assembly (TSA) sequence database 80 were downloaded.",
    "Transdecoder (https://github.com/TransDecoder/ TransDecoder) was used to extract the protein sequences from transcriptomes."
  ]
}